{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ba424c621d","title":"毛泽东给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13c61d1fbe","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"ba424c621d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d4db0f1008","type":"title","text":"毛泽东给周世钊的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"840831d936","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"455bf53df6","type":"appellation","text":"敦元学长兄：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"061d06df33","type":"paragraph","text":"迭接电示，又得九月二十八日长书，勤勤恳恳，如见故人。延安曾接大示，寄重庆的信则未收到。兄过去虽未参加革命斗争，教书就是有益于人民的。城南学社诸友来电亦已收到，请兄转告他们，感谢他们的好意。兄为一师校长，深庆得人，可见骏骨未凋，尚有生气。倘有可能，尊著旧诗尚祈抄寄若干，多多益善。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"41256d46fa","type":"paragraph","text":"除台湾。西藏外，全国各地大约几个月内即可完成军事占领。但大难甫平，民生憔悴，须有效年时间，方能恢复人民经济，完成土地制度的改革及提高人民政治觉悟水平，这些任务均有待于文教工作的协助。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"ab0e6527ca","type":"paragraph","text":"陈泽同先生的意见书已收阅，当交此间工业机关研究，请兄为我代致谢意。他的工作问题请告他直接向湖南当局要求解决，不要等候我的答复。谨此奉复。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"15ecff7e94","type":"paragraph","text":"敬颂","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"200e6c6037","type":"appellation","text":"教祺","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"},{"id":"859eb6395e","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛  泽  东一九四九年十月十五日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ba424c621d"}],"page":{"id":"e568e11254","publica